OL,7,F"The media recruits graduates from the
OL,8,Farts, humanities, and they tend to be
OL,9,Fmetropolitan and to have a point of
OL,10,Fview you could describe as liberal
OL,11,Fcentre, centre left. We kind of
OL,12,Freflect that," he told The Times.
OL,14,FThe corporation has faced a backlash
OL,15,Fover its coverage of the the Israel-
OL,16,FHamas conflict and it recently emerged
OL,17,Fthat a documentary it aired about Gaza
OL,18,Ffeatured the son of a senior Hamas
OL,19,Ffigure.
