OL,7,FA protest was held outside
OL,8,FBroadcasting House on Thursday with
OL,9,Fdemonstrators claiming the BBC had
OL,10,Faired Hamas propaganda.
OL,12,F"We make mistakes in our journalism.
OL,13,FWe correct mistakes", Mr Shah said.
OL,15,FHe added: "There needs to be greater
OL,16,Faccountability. People have to face
OL,17,Fthe consequences of what they do."
