OL,7,FMr Shah also spoke about the
OL,8,Fimportance of diversity and said the
OL,9,FBBC "needs to do a lot more to ensure
OL,10,Four staff reflects the country as a
OL,11,Fwhole. We need more variety and
OL,12,Fdiversity".
OL,14,FExpanding on this, he said: "More
OL,15,Fdiversity of thought. It's on,
OL,16,Ffrankly, the northern working class
OL,17,Fwhere we're poor. That's where the
OL,18,Ffocus should be."
