OL,7,FMr Shah has been in his role since
OL,8,FMarch 2024 and said he was "surprised
OL,9,Fin my first year at having this
OL,10,Fprocession of men" who have had
OL,11,Fallegations made against them.
OL,13,FThese include former newsreader Huw
OL,14,FEdwards and Russell Brand, who had a
OL,15,FRadio 2 show in the noughties.
OL,17,F"The theme that keeps coming through
OL,18,Fis that junior staff are vulnerable to
OL,19,Fbeing preyed on by people with power.
OL,20,FWe have to stop it," he said.
