OL,7,F"I will not tolerate junior staff
OL,8,Fbeing scared to report what's
OL,9,Fhappening or their managers looking
OL,10,Fthe other way."
OL,12,FHe added: "We need to have some way of
OL,13,Fpreserving whistleblowers' anonymity,
OL,14,Fso we can throw people out and do it
OL,15,Fquickly. I'm absolutely determined.
OL,16,FThis is a cancer we need to cut out."
