OL,7,FIn January, a BBC review into the
OL,8,Fconduct of Brand during his time with
OL,9,Fthe broadcaster found a number of
OL,10,Fpeople "felt unable to raise" concerns
OL,11,Fabout the presenter and believed he
OL,12,F"would always get his way and
OL,13,Ftherefore they stayed silent".
OL,15,FLast year, Edwards was handed a
OL,16,Fsuspended sentence after admitting
OL,17,Fthree charges of "making" indecent
OL,18,Fphotographs after he was sent 41
OL,19,Fillegal images by convicted paedophile
OL,20,FAlex Williams over WhatsApp.
